channel.title: Does Hamchi work with No-Ip? [Hurry up 'foo!]
channel.description:
Ok, I have No-Ip up and everything, and it says warmwaddlescape.servegame.com is up. But people can only get on through my Hamachi I.P., and not the No-Ip I.P. Does anyone know if there is a way to make it work, and if there is tell me?
[shadow=red,left]Lol hurry up people[/shadow] [size=6pt]I like chocolate![/size]

item.title: Does Hamchi work with No-Ip? [Hurry up 'foo!]
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Yes, I believe you can. Go into Your No-ip and do the steps you would usually do, except in the “Ip address” spot, type in your hamachi ip address.
